      "value": "SOURCED. Distinct OPN appropriation (1810N) established by PL 116-93 (Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2020) for private contracted CONUS surface + submarine maintenance at CPF / FFC. Same avail vocabulary as OMN 1B4B (OH, SRA, PIA, P-MA, RA/TA, CIA, DPIA, DSRA, SCO -- defined OPN_BA1_Book lines 21217-21268). FY25 enacted $2,392.190M -- replaces prior $500M plug (4.8x underweight). No double-count vs OMN 1B4B: 1810N OPN is parallel funding stream to 1804N OMN."
