    {
      "ref": "H10",
      "style": "S_DEFAULT",
      "value": "PLAN ESTIMATE - genuinely not source-pinnable. WPN_Book P-40 exhibits structure WPN as missile/torpedo procurement (BA01 Ballistic Missiles $1.80B, BA02 Other Missiles $3.40B, BA03 Torpedoes $0.74B, BA04 Other Weapons $0.17B, BA06 Spares $0.24B FY25). Mods lines (Trident II Mods $1.79B, Tomahawk Mods $0.30B, etc.) are weapons-system-level sustainment, not ship depot work. Shipboard installation flows under separate (typically OMN) contracts and is not isolable from WPN P-40s. The $500M plug is a judgment estimate of WPN $ that flows to FPDS combat-systems-related MRO PSCs."
